>>>>>>> ### Find out what reports have been published in the latest audits of
diabetes care in England and Wales and download and read our easy-to-read
versions aimed at people with diabetes and the general public.
>>>>>>> Latest information on data collection and reports are available from
>>>>>>> * The NDA Core Audit 2018-19 report on care processes and
treatment targets in England and Wales was published in December 2020.
>>>>>>> * The annual report on the Diabetes Prevention Programme
(DPP) and non-diabetic hyperglycaemia 2018-19 was published in November 2020.
